+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
+                    project Admin                        +
+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++

create a group 'projectAdmin'
each member of this group is able to edit or delete all 
created projects

also the chosen coordinator of a project is able to manage 
his project 

+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
+                    management                           +
+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++

the projects-app is required for running the other apps
projecthours is needed to manage job
projectbilling is needed to create invoices
projectstatistics creates user- and projectstats
projectdelivery manages delivery notes 

  